          "tag": "1. Sıfatları -> Fiile Çevirme:",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF0000\">get</font> + <font color=\"#FFFF00\">Sıfat</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>My son <font color=\"#FF0000\">got</font> <font color=\"#FFFF00\">big</font>: Oğlum büyüdü.</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF0000\">make</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">somone</font> + <font color=\"#FFFF00\">Sıfat</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>You <font color=\"#FF0000\">made</font> <font color=\"#00FF00\">me</font> <font color=\"#FFFF00\">angry</font> : Beni sinirlendirdin.</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF0000\">make</font> + <font color=\"#BA55D3\">something</font> + <font color=\"#FFFF00\">Sıfat</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Inflation <font color=\"#FF0000\">makes</font> the prices of <font color=\"#BA55D3\">everyting</font> <font color=\"#FFFF00\">more expensive</font></td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "color": "pink",
          "tag": "2. Fiillerden -> Fiil yapma (Kime yaptırdığının önemi yoksa):",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF0000\">get</font> + <font color=\"#BA55D3\">something</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V3</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Ayşe <font color=\"#FF0000\">got</font> <font color=\"#BA55D3\">her hair</font> <font color=\"#00FFFF\">done</font> : Ayşe saçlarını yaptırttı.</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF0000\">have</font> + <font color=\"#BA55D3\">something</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V3</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>I <font color=\"#FF0000\">had</font> <font color=\"#BA55D3\">my car</font> <font color=\"#00FFFF\">fixed</font> : Arabamı tamir ettirttim.</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "color": "amber",
          "tag": "3. Fiillerden -> Fiil yapma (Zorlama YOK!):",
          "text": "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size:14px;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #eee;'><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>FORMÜL</th><th style='text-align:left; padding:8px;'>ÖRNEK</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF0000\">get</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">someone</font> + (to) <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V1</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>Ayşe <font color=\"#FF0000\">got</font> <font color=\"#00FF00\">hairdresser</font> (to) <font color=\"#00FFFF\">do</font> her <font color=\"#BA55D3\">dair</font></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px;'><font color=\"#FF0000\">have</font> + <font color=\"#00FF00\">someone</font> + <font color=\"#00FFFF\">V1</font></td><td style='padding:8px;'>I <font color=\"#FF0000\">had</font> <font color=\"#00FF00\">the dentist</font> <font color=\"#00FFFF\">pull</font> <font color=\"#BA55D3\">my tooth</font></td></tr></tbody></table><br><b>Not:</b> Sınava gireceksen ‘’get’’ kullanılırken gramer olarak (+ to V1) kullanılır. Ama günlük konuşmada V1 kullan geç!"
        },
